question: Where can I find restaurant heading towards Triangle Disc Care, Raleigh, NC from the providence dog park, Raleigh, NC, within a radius of 190 kilometers?
sql:
WITH
    angle AS (SELECT degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.796552 35.897057)',4326)::geography, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.701767 35.81502)',4326)::geography)) AS value)
SELECT * FROM pois,angle
WHERE amenity = 'restaurant'
AND ST_DWithin(pois.geometry, ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.796552 35.897057)',4326)::geography, 190000)
AND (degrees(ST_Azimuth(ST_GeomFromText('POINT (-78.796552 35.897057)',4326)::geography, pois.geometry)) BETWEEN angle.value - 22.5 AND angle.value + 22.5);
